Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.39,0:44:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the neurotransmitters. We know that the neurotransmitters get depressed so that when you remove the\Ndrugs there's a depression of neurotransmitters which therefore causes depression. So there
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.35,0:44:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is the brain enzyme and the brain neurotransmitter explanation.\NBut that's insufficient. We see now what we're addicted to. There's a certain level
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.59,0:44:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness. In the beginning it begins to work but it then starts a process. A process\Nin which we begin to go down because despite all of our education we say, no, it is a drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.97,0:45:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That begins to create a negative energy field within us. Within us. The drugs themselves\Nand the whole scene in which they occur are a negative energy field scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.94,0:45:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what characterizes a negative energy field? Well, we said pride. So we take one\Nof these groups and I did it just before we started to do this phase and calibrated what
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.00,0:45:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is the energy field of that group and we found it was a hundred and eighty in a negative\Ndirection. So what kind of a phase would we expect from a person that's a hundred and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.62,0:45:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,eighty reverse attitude? Upped, nerd, arrogant, denial, contemptuous and anti-life. Anti-life\Nwouldn't you say that this is anti-life wouldn't you say that to encourage
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.67,0:45:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,people to ingest that which destroys every aspect of your life is that which\Ndoes not support life all right now begin to see what the destruction of the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.00,0:46:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,energy field is so even if I recover from drugs let's say and I sit around\Nlistening to that music we saw with kinesiology that what happens is the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.85,0:46:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,music creates a destructive energy field over on the right you'll see what\Ncomes out of this is destruction the process coming out of the bottom of the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.38,0:46:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,reverse energy field is to seek destruction it begins to create an\Nunconscious guilt and an unconscious self-hatred because unconsciously you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.00,0:46:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot destroy yourself without creating guilt the peculiar thing about a\Nnegative energy field is that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.41,0:46:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the person begins to seek and desire destruction therefore to tell somebody\Nyou know who is in this kind of an energy field that if you continue to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.68,0:47:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,drink or use drugs you know you will end up destroyed the person says good\Nsomething within the person just loves it I mean it sounds so dramatic you know
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.18,0:47:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember watching Lost Weekend I had a half pint in my bottle you know in\Nmy pocket in the movie and as I'm watching Lost Weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.46,0:47:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you know I'm drinking and I watched this guy's destruction and you know if\Nyou've ever seen Lost Weekend he's got the DTs he goes insane he ends up in a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.42,0:47:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,straitjacket he was telling me my own future anyways I watched it I was like\Ncaught by the glamour of it seemed to me almost glamorous you know there was a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.34,0:47:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,seduction and attraction to going downhill weird sick perverted right what\Ndoes the word pervert mean it means that we're going down the hill we're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.18,0:47:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,be\Ndriving goods when we know we're going to be back to them and you know which was
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.66,0:47:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,healthy and that which was positive that which was innocent and loving has been\Ntwitted somehow even the names of some groups are called twisted you know that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.06,0:48:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that is exactly clinically correct it does twist from this direction to this\Ndirection what happens when a person goes in this direction is that they
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.72,0:48:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,desire that which is destructive I discovered that years ago we saw that\Nwhen people listen to this kind of music they spend six or seven days a week
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.13,0:48:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to get to the bottom of a bed they don't realize that they're not\Nsick so they have to stay awake and keep trying and pray until the morning comes
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.77,0:48:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,morning after a meal they eat well and eat food they eat and drink and drink that\Nwent all night I'm healthy I'm happy like the President says all the time I'm happy
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.85,0:48:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With kinesiology, if you hold a substance over the solar plexus and test a person's\Nenergy, it will tell whether it is good for you or bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.19,0:48:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would put things in little brown envelopes.\NIn a normal state, for instance, let's say pesticides will make you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.47,0:48:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if I play that kind of music so that the energy field goes in this direction, still\Nholding the pesticide, that which is poisonous, and I test the person, they will go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.71,0:48:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird.\NWhen I first saw that, it scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.73,0:48:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It scared me, but then I saw the implications and I got it.\NIt's like it totally reversed the person in there and now backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.55,0:49:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field around the body, called the etheric body, the etheric body is like an\Nenergy blueprint of the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.97,0:49:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens is it turns these fields around.\NAnd now the consciousness of the person is dominated by a desire for destruction, a desire
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.83,0:49:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for destruction.\NSo what these energy fields created by all these groups and by these drugs and all their
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.39,0:49:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,expressions, what it's inviting you to do is to destroy yourself and then to enjoy the\Nprocess.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.16,0:49:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the process of destroying yourself.\NSo we invite you to destroy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.16,0:49:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the process of destroying yourself.\NEnjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.78,0:49:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it look like destruction when you're in this kind of an energy field?\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.81,0:49:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks attractive.\NIt looks glamorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.81,0:49:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See, seduction comes right into here.\NThis is the energy field of seduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.01,0:50:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're talking about now is the utilization of seduction, seduction through pleasurable\Nsensation, through drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.69,0:50:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So seduction to inculcate, like brainwash the person into becoming the victim of that.\NIt's like I say, join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.85,0:50:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Join me.\NSo pleasurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.30,0:50:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.\NOh, it feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.64,0:50:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.64,0:50:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I got you.\NNow I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.76,0:50:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're mine.\NThat's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.28,0:50:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what's going on when you see it.\NIt's so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.05,0:50:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so clear.\NIt's so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.15,0:50:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so clear.\NIt's so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.15,0:50:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so clear.\NIt's so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.63,0:50:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so clear.\NIt's so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.63,0:50:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.\NIt's so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.31,0:50:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so clear.\NIt's so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.11,0:50:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so clear.\NAt least you know what's going on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.11,0:50:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At least you can't say, well, I didn't know.\NYou know?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.11,0:51:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know I was being seduced.\NI didn't know that I was being overwhelmed by a very powerful negative energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.09,0:51:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that it was beginning to dominate my conscious and that I became the victim of that.\NThat's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.56,0:51:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All we experience in our unconsciousness, and the purpose of this is to make you conscious\Nrather than unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.72,0:51:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All we experienced was the destruction.\NAll we knew was we kept getting high, and somehow our life was falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.87,0:51:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't understand how, so we'd say, well, I'm only going to smoke grass after this.\NI mean, I'm off the hard stuff, or I'm only going to drink beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.07,0:51:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only going to have a couple of beers before bed, you see?\NHow is it just a couple of beers before bed ended up as a case a day, the same as it used
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.77,0:51:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to be, and then a quarter a day, and then adding the fills and the ups and the downs\Nin order to be able to keep the body walking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.29,0:52:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the solution of this?\NWell, the solution of it begins with an understanding, with an understanding to just get what I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.78,0:52:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,saying today.\NI don't care what you do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.20,0:52:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in that.\NOnce we begin to understand, see, this energy field of love, the purpose, the purpose, the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.00,0:52:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,intention that comes out of the energy field of love is to understand, not to condemn or\Nto make wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.90,0:52:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in right or wrong.\NNo interest in condemnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.20,0:52:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?\NCompassion, what that has to do with is the ultimate understanding, to understand what
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.10,0:52:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is the process, to look around you, and now that you're more awake, see, what is the process\Ngoing on in the lives of the people around you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.16,0:52:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no longer, once you get de-glamorized, it's no longer glamorous.\NYou walk into the so-called happy hour, happy, hysterically.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.63,0:52:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke that is.\NYou walk in the nearest bar and grill where it says, happy hour, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.11,0:53:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,People zonked out, staring at television, totally unconscious, in their mind, glamorized\Nby the thought that this is cocktail time, and I'm having a happy hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.69,0:53:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this is great, being amongst the guys, you see?\NFriday night, paycheck time, everybody congregates, and now we get into the glamor of comradhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.48,0:53:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the pseudo-glamor of pseudo-bridegrooming.\NBrotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.16,0:53:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pseudo-brotherhood.\NHow do you know it's pseudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.16,0:53:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you quit drinking and you quit hanging out with those people, and doing what\Nthey're doing, they ain't gonna want to hear from you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.47,0:53:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A true brother is somebody who, when they see that you're having a problem with it,\Nsupports to get in office.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.71,0:53:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A true brother is somebody who really loves you, can see, man, you're throwing up with\Nthat stuff all the time, you've cracked up the car with that stuff all the time, you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.35,0:53:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,know, the wife is starting to walk out on you all the time, because they haven't got\Nwhat they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.91,0:53:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're blowing it all here.\NA real friend would help you get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.91,0:54:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a real friend.\NThat's somebody who's in an energy field like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.91,0:54:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So seek those people out.\NFind those people who have found the way out, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.91,0:54:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,People willing to share the truth.\NHere's a great guy, you know, I don't know him, but his willingness to share the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.96,0:54:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,his willingness to come out and say, yeah, this is what happened.\NWhat he does is he lends us his energy, the knowledge that he's gained through his own
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.00,0:54:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.\NSo we seek out the people, you know, who have beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.95,0:54:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?\NBecause those people are all coming out of this energy field of 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.95,0:54:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All these self-help groups, cocaine anonymous, alcohol anonymous, narcotics anonymous, all\Nthose 12-step groups, all based on the same 12 steps of truth, are coming out of an energy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.95,0:54:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,field of 540.\NAn energy field of 540 is what you've got to be in to beat the drug and alcohol problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.95,0:55:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To hang out in a reversed energy field of 190 then means that your consciousness is\Ndominated by that field.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.32,0:55:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw with kinesiology, it had nothing to do with her willpower.\NIt had nothing to do with his willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.32,0:55:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person says, well, I'm going to handle this with willpower.\NAll right, let's see you resist it with willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.32,0:55:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I never found a person yet.\NWillpower doesn't have the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.32,0:55:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a love power.\NThat which is truly loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.32,0:55:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is willing to truly share the truth with you.\NThe person is willing to really stand up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.32,0:55:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up for what aspect of you.\NNot join with your wish to destroy yourself, but to join with that which is nurturing and
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.32,0:55:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,supporting.\NThat which is forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.15,0:55:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What people will get is they'll make wrong about drugs and alcohol.\NWho cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.15,0:55:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Make wrong is coming down here from a prideful opinion.\NYou know, I'm right because I don't use, and you're wrong because you use.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.15,0:56:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not helpful.\NYou see, if guilt could handle it, if guilt could handle it, then all the millions of
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.15,0:56:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,people who drive and die from drugs and alcohol wouldn't be dying because they all feel guilty\Nabout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.15,0:56:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconscious guilt is what leads the person to go off the bottom of the box in the first\Nplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.15,0:56:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So feeling guilty about drugs and alcohol isn't going to be the answer.\NThe unconscious guilt is what leads to the path of suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.15,0:56:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see all these people like you rolling the tire over a few times.\NEnded up in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.15,0:56:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonder to him he's still alive.\NAll the deaths due to overdoses and all are not overdoses at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.33,0:56:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If we check them out, we'll find that the negative energy field leads to the unconscious\Nwish for death.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.65,0:56:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The unconscious attraction of that which is destruction.\NAnd so it's not an accidental overdose.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.65,0:56:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All the famous rock stars.\NAre you telling me they're amateurs?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.65,0:56:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're experts.\NJust like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.65,0:57:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I was.\NI managed to physically survive right at the very point of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.65,0:57:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole life flipped around.\NI went from max here to max up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.65,0:57:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened it up and I said, if there's a God, I ask him to help me.\NI was an atheist at the time and had been for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.65,0:57:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly I stood in an infinite presence and it blew out drugs, alcohol, and any desire\Nfrom them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.65,0:57:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now and forever.\NNor have they ever arisen in 22 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.65,0:57:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens then is that the effect progressively of the drugs and alcohol on the human body\Nis to drive us further and further down.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.20,0:57:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Until finally that attraction of death, that attraction, expresses itself as the overdose.\NThe accidental overdose.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.20,0:57:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We were expert psychopharmacologists.\NI had to juggle in a day 42 pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.20,0:57:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I averaged 40 pills a day.\NPlus a pint to afford a booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.20,0:57:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus anything I could smoke, drink, or inject to put in myself in any other way.\NEt cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.20,0:57:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A pair of Gorex and Serpent Hydrate with codeine.\NA couple of alcohols.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.20,0:57:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'd go to bed.\NAnd I'd go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.68,0:57:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd go to bed.\NAnd I'd go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.68,0:57:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd go to bed.\NAnd I'd go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.68,0:57:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd go to bed.\NAnd I'd go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.68,0:57:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd go to bed.\NAnd I'd go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.68,0:57:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of ampoules.\NYou name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.68,0:57:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever I could get.\NThrow in a Demerol and a couple of martinis on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.76,0:58:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How could there be an accidental overdose with somebody who knows how to juggle everything\Nlike that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.00,0:58:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing such thing is accidental.\NSo turning over the car, getting mugged, getting robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.10,0:58:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Robbed.\NGot spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.54,0:58:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Got sent in.\Nskull fractured in a fight that is the coming out of the passive suicide not actively sought
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.68,0:58:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,consciously but unconsciously so that is the effect of that energy field that's the whole\Nenergy field that we're talking about today now you have some way of comprehending and understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.24,0:58:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,why is it despite this guy's thing his brilliance his creativity his obvious integrity that he\Nthat he once had how did it all get destroyed he himself says it's impersonal and we see today
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.49,0:59:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that that is impersonal you see the effect that we saw there when we tested with kinesiology\Nthat's impersonal that's the effect of an energy field it has nothing to do with willpower your
