Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.78,0:59:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is as big as the city block and they turn the power on you are going to be at the effect of\Nthat isn't that right even your belt buckles going to pull you one way or the other now we
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.86,1:00:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,can switch the polarity of that field we can make this pole negative this pole positive now by\Nthrowing a switch we can reverse it that's exactly what happened we were born and we grew up in a
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.18,1:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,positive nurturing electromagnetic field in this direction then what happened is something came\Ninto our life and what positive in the negative suddenly so what happens is the person goes in
